       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 46 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
         fhir:index 0 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "libraryName" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "IMMZD18SDTPDelayedOrInterruptedSeriesLogic" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 1 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "name" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "DTP dose 1 (delayed start) Create" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 2 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "statement" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/*\n@output: DTP dose 1 (delayed start) Create\n@create: For children whose vaccination series has been interrupted, the series should be resumed without repeating previous doses. Children aged 1 year to under 7 years who have not previously been vaccinated should receive 3 doses of vaccine following a 0, 1, 6 month schedule.\n\nIf tetanus vaccination is started during adolescence or adulthood, a total of only 5 appropriately spaced doses are required to obtain lifelong protection.\n\nPregnant women and their newborn infants are protected from birth-associated tetanus if the mother received 5 doses if first vaccinated during adolescence/adulthood.\n*/\ndefine \"DTP dose 1 (delayed start) Create\":\n  if \"DTP dose 1 (delayed start)\"\n  then 'For children whose vaccination series has been interrupted, the series should be resumed without repeating previous doses. Children aged 1 year to under 7 years who have not previously been vaccinated should receive 3 doses of vaccine following a 0, 1, 6 month schedule.\nIf tetanus vaccination is started during adolescence or adulthood, a total of only 5 appropriately spaced doses are required to obtain lifelong protection.\nPregnant women and their newborn infants are protected from birth-associated tetanus if the mother received 5 doses if first vaccinated during adolescence/adulthood.' + '\nDue Date: ' + ToString(\"DTP dose 1 (delayed start) Due Date\")\n  else ''" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 3 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "displaySequence" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueInteger [ fhir:value "46"^^xsd:integer ]
       ] ;
       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 47 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
